snippet.title: Monaco 2 Dev Log #1
snippet.description:
Monaco 2 is in development!
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1063030/Monaco_2
Discord: http://discord.gg/pocketwatch
Twitch: http://twitch.tv/pocketwatch

What IS Monaco 2? Our first development log answers that question, in addition to showing off concept art and giving you a sneak peak (listen?) to composer Austin Wintory's work in progress on the game's musical score.
